AndroidManifest: Remove nonexistent OpenVPN activities

The *.ovpn association in particular was causing FCs.

Signed-off-by: Kevin Cernekee <cernekee@gmail.com>

Use base64 to store binary data in profiles

Storing raw PKCS#12 files in the XML profile was probably not such a
great idea and seems to be causing problems for certificate users.  Let's
encode them as base64, and autodetect the format when reading them back
in.

Signed-off-by: Kevin Cernekee <cernekee@gmail.com>
